name: come here
description:
they never could get a moment where they could be alone.. only spared enough time to share a glance in passing, silence was becoming so common. the tension that thickened between them did all the talking necessary. 

biting lips thinking about him despite being so easily accessible drove her mad. when she could, she would watch from afar while he went about his daily task of punishing his subjects.. he was so firm and precise in the way he commanded, the way he made women bend to his will. not with ego, but with rigor and care. she was paying attention for long enough to get lost.. long enough that it took her a few seconds to realize she was caught when he locked eyes with her. 

"were you watching me?" he asked.

"come here."
